\": 4007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Owens has proven to be a valuable supporter in Biles' life, standing by her after she decided to pull out of the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 4014, \"to\": 4142, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Owens\", \"from\": 4014, \"to\": 4019}, {\"ngram\": \"a valuable supporter\", \"from\": 4037, \"to\": 4057}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles' life\", \"from\": 4061, \"to\": 4072}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 4123, \"to\": 4141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Your strength and courage is unmatched and you inspire me more and more everyday,\\\" he wrote on social media following her withdrawal from the competition.\", \"from\": 4143, \"to\": 4298, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your strength\", \"from\": 4144, \"to\": 4157}, {\"ngram\": \"courage\", \"from\": 4162, \"to\": 4169}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 4239, \"to\": 4251}, {\"ngram\": \"her withdrawal\", \"from\": 4262, \"to\": 4276}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 4282, \"to\": 4297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This exit from the Games proved to be a huge turning point for Biles, both mentally and physically.\", \"from\": 4300, \"to\": 4399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This exit\", \"from\": 4300, \"to\": 4309}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 4315, \"to\": 4324}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge turning point\", \"from\": 4338, \"to\": 4358}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 4363, \"to\": 4368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After winning an impressive stack of gold medals at World Championship competitions in 2018 and 2019, the gymnast looked to be on top form ahead of her second Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 4400, \"to\": 4573, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an impressive stack\", \"from\": 4414, \"to\": 4433}, {\"ngram\": \"gold medals\", \"from\": 4437, \"to\": 4448}, {\"ngram\": \"World Championship competitions\", \"from\": 4452, \"to\": 4483}, {\"ngram\": \"the gymnast\", \"from\": 4502, \"to\": 4513}, {\"ngram\": \"top form\", \"from\": 4530, \"to\": 4538}, {\"ngram\": \"her second Olympic Games\", \"from\": 4548, \"to\": 4572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She started strong, helping her team qualify for the final and advancing in all individual disciplines - the only athlete to do so.\", \"from\": 4574, \"to\": 4705, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her team\", \"from\": 4602, \"to\": 4610}, {\"ngram\": \"all individual disciplines\", \"from\": 4650, \"to\": 4676}, {\"ngram\": \"the only athlete\", \"from\": 4679, \"to\": 4695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the pressure of being at the top weighed heavily on the young athlete, and her mental health took a knock.\", \"from\": 4707, \"to\": 4822, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 4716, \"to\": 4728}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 4741, \"to\": 4748}, {\"ngram\": \"the young athlete\", \"from\": 4768, \"to\": 4785}, {\"ngram\": \"her mental health\", \"from\": 4791, \"to\": 4808}, {\"ngram\": \"a knock\", \"from\": 4814, \"to\": 4821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I truly do feel like I have the weight of the world on my shoulders at times,\\\" she wrote on social media.\", \"from\": 4823, \"to\": 4929, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the weight\", \"from\": 4852, \"to\": 4862}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 4866, \"to\": 4875}, {\"ngram\": \"my shoulders\", \"from\": 4879, \"to\": 4891}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 4895, \"to\": 4900}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 4916, \"to\": 4928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know I brush it off and make it seem like pressure does not affect me but damn sometimes it's hard\\\".\", \"from\": 4930, \"to\": 5033, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 4975, \"to\": 4983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following several mistakes in her routines, it was revealed that Biles was suffering from a condition known in the industry as \\\"the twisties\\\".\", \"from\": 5035, \"to\": 5177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"several mistakes\", \"from\": 5045, \"to\": 5061}, {\"ngram\": \"her routines\", \"from\": 5065, \"to\": 5077}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 5100, \"to\": 5105}, {\"ngram\": \"a condition\", \"from\": 5125, \"to\": 5136}, {\"ngram\": \"the industry\", \"from\": 5146, \"to\": 5158}, {\"ngram\": \"the twisties\", \"from\": 5163, \"to\": 5175}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Comparable to the \\\"yips\\\" in golf, the twisties occur when a gymnast experiences a sudden and catastrophic mental block - sometimes right in the middle of soaring through the air.\", \"from\": 5179, \"to\": 5357, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the \\\"yips\", \"from\": 5193, \"to\": 5202}, {\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 5207, \"to\": 5211}, {\"ngram\": \"the twisties\", \"from\": 5213, \"to\": 5225}, {\"ngram\": \"a gymnast\", \"from\": 5237, \"to\": 5246}, {\"ngram\": \"a sudden and catastrophic mental block\", \"from\": 5259, \"to\": 5297}, {\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 5319, \"to\": 5329}, {\"ngram\": \"the air\", \"from\": 5349, \"to\": 5356}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the pressure just got too much,\\\" British gymnast Claudia Fragapane told the BBC after Biles' struggles.\", \"from\": 5359, \"to\": 5471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5401, \"end\": 5408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.6259691167294671, \"rank\": 0.5975225408266017, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 5417, \"end\": 5434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Claudia_Fragapane\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Claudia Fragapane\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Claudia_Fragapane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Claudia_Fragapane\"}, {\"begin\": 5444, \"end\": 5447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9999994203755566, \"rank\": 5.531776154343527e-07, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 5368, \"to\": 5380}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles' struggles\", \"from\": 5454, \"to\": 5470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's really dangerous if you doubt yourself\\\".\", \"from\": 5472, \"to\": 5518, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After missing several difficult and technical moves, Biles decided to withdraw from the Olympic Games entirely.\", \"from\": 5520, \"to\": 5631, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"several difficult and technical moves\", \"from\": 5534, \"to\": 5571}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 5573, \"to\": 5578}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 5604, \"to\": 5621}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She told reporters: \\\"I have to put my pride aside.\", \"from\": 5632, \"to\": 5682, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 5641, \"to\": 5650}, {\"ngram\": \"my pride\", \"from\": 5667, \"to\": 5675}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have to do what's right for me and focus on my mental health.\\\"\", \"from\": 5683, \"to\": 5747, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mental health\", \"from\": 5729, \"to\": 5745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athlete was praised for opening the conversation around mental health in elite sports, however she told Vanity Fair that she did not see herself as a role model.\", \"from\": 5749, \"to\": 5914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5857, \"end\": 5868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanity_Fair_(magazine)\", \"score\": 0.9083471797491343, \"rank\": 0.09190153882043064, \"text\": \"Vanity Fair\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanity_Fair_(mag