 \"from\": 6139, \"to\": 6151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everything that happened, it's a trauma response\\\" she explains in the new film.\", \"from\": 6160, \"to\": 6240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a trauma response\", \"from\": 6192, \"to\": 6209}, {\"ngram\": \"the new film\", \"from\": 6227, \"to\": 6239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As well as being forthcoming about her battles with mental health, Biles has been outspoken about the abuse she faced under USA Gymnastics physician Larry Nassar.\", \"from\": 6242, \"to\": 6404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6366, \"end\": 6380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.197901971862627e-15, \"text\": \"USA Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\"}, {\"begin\": 6391, \"end\": 6403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\", \"score\": 0.887322554629349, \"rank\": 0.12698589118819217, \"text\": \"Larry Nassar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2159907\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her battles\", \"from\": 6277, \"to\": 6288}, {\"ngram\": \"mental health\", \"from\": 6294, \"to\": 6307}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 6309, \"to\": 6314}, {\"ngram\": \"the abuse\", \"from\": 6340, \"to\": 6349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2018, encouraged by the momentum of the Me Too movement, Biles revealed on Twitter (now X) that Nassar had sexually assaulted her.\", \"from\": 6405, \"to\": 6538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6483, \"end\": 6490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1596222503871459e-49, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}, {\"begin\": 6504, \"end\": 6510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.429304318904377e-94, \"text\": \"Nassar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2159907\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the momentum\", \"from\": 6428, \"to\": 6440}, {\"ngram\": \"the Me Too movement\", \"from\": 6444, \"to\": 6463}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 6465, \"to\": 6470}, {\"ngram\": \"now X\", \"from\": 6492, \"to\": 6497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the subsequent trial, the court heard 156 women and girls testify of their abuse under Nassar, and he was sentenced to 40 to 175 years in prison.\", \"from\": 6540, \"to\": 6692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6634, \"end\": 6640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.429304318904377e-94, \"text\": \"Nassar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2159907\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the subsequent trial\", \"from\": 6547, \"to\": 6567}, {\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 6569, \"to\": 6578}, {\"ngram\": \"156 women\", \"from\": 6585, \"to\": 6594}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 6599, \"to\": 6604}, {\"ngram\": \"their abuse\", \"from\": 6616, \"to\": 6627}, {\"ngram\": \"40 to 175 years\", \"from\": 6666, \"to\": 6681}, {\"ngram\": \"prison\", \"from\": 6685, \"to\": 6691}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2020, Netflix released a documentary called Athlete A which follows the investigation into Nassar's abuse.\", \"from\": 6694, \"to\": 6803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6703, \"end\": 6710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3879565972584475e-27, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http:/