vere, but I never should have been left alone to suffer the abuse of Larry Nassar.\", \"from\": 7419, \"to\": 7542, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7529, \"end\": 7541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\", \"score\": 0.887322554629349, \"rank\": 0.12698589118819217, \"text\": \"Larry Nassar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2159907\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a strong individual\", \"from\": 7424, \"to\": 7443}, {\"ngram\": \"the abuse\", \"from\": 7516, \"to\": 7525}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the only reason I did, was because of the failures that lie at the heart of the abuse that you are now asked to investigate.\\\"\", \"from\": 7543, \"to\": 7672, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only reason\", \"from\": 7547, \"to\": 7562}, {\"ngram\": \"the failures\", \"from\": 7585, \"to\": 7597}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 7610, \"to\": 7619}, {\"ngram\": \"the abuse\", \"from\": 7623, \"to\": 7632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After posting \\\"hurtful comments\\\" about Biles and her Olympic teammates in June, former Team USA gymnast MyKayla Skinner cited abuse within the gymnastics industry as the root cause.\", \"from\": 7674, \"to\": 7855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7761, \"end\": 7769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.996735634354881, \"rank\": 0.003274351276844965, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 7778, \"end\": 7793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MyKayla_Skinner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"MyKayla Skinner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MyKayla_Skinner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MyKayla_Skinner\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hurtful comments\", \"from\": 7689, \"to\": 7705}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 7713, \"to\": 7718}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic teammates\", \"from\": 7723, \"to\": 7744}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 7748, \"to\": 7752}, {\"ngram\": \"abuse\", \"from\": 7800, \"to\": 7805}, {\"ngram\": \"the gymnastics industry\", \"from\": 7813, \"to\": 7836}, {\"ngram\": \"the root cause\", \"from\": 7840, \"to\": 7854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a video posted to YouTube, Skinner had said: \\\"Besides Simone, I feel like the talent and the depth just is not like what it used to be.\\\"\", \"from\": 7856, \"to\": 7995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7877, \"end\": 7884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6979519656607225e-16, \"text\": \"YouTube\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a video\", \"from\": 7859, \"to\": 7866}, {\"ngram\": \"Skinner\", \"from\": 7886, \"to\": 7893}, {\"ngram\": \"Simone\", \"from\": 7913, \"to\": 7919}, {\"ngram\": \"the talent\", \"from\": 7933, \"to\": 7943}, {\"ngram\": \"the depth\", \"from\": 7948, \"to\": 7957}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She went on to add: \\\"A lot of girls do not work as hard.\", \"from\": 7997, \"to\": 8053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 8018, \"to\": 8023}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 8027, \"to\": 8032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The girls just do not have the work ethic.\\\"\", \"from\": 8054, \"to\": 8097, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The girls\", \"from\": 8054, \"to\": 8063}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 8081, \"to\": 8089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following backlash, Skinner then apologised for her comments, saying: \\\"I am coming to terms that I have not fully dealt with the emotional and verbal abuse I endured under [gymnastics coach] Marta [K\\u00e1rolyi] that perhaps led to my hurtful comments.\", \"from\": 8099, \"to\": 8346, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"backlash\", \"from\": 8109, \"to\": 8117}, {\"ngram\": \"Skinner\", \"from\": 8119, \"to\": 8126}, {\"ngram\": \"her comments\", \"from\": 8147, \"to\": 8159}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 8185, \"to\": 8190}, {\"ngram\": \"the emotional and verbal abuse\", \"from\": 8224, \"to\": 8254}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics coach\", \"from\": 8272, \"to\": 8288}, {\"ngram\": \"[K\\u00e1rolyi\", \"from\": 8296, \"to\": 8304}, {\"ngram\": \"my hurtful comments\", \"from\": 8326, \"to\": 8345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I take full responsibility for what I said and I deeply apologise.\\\"\", \"from\": 8347, \"to\": 8414, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"full responsibility\", \"from\": 8354, \"to\": 8373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"[sic] Biles and her teammates swiftly blocked Skinner on all social media platforms, but the comments clearly left their mark.\", \"from\": 8415, \"to\": 8542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 8421, \"to\": 8426}, {\"ngram\": \"her teammates\", \"from\": 8431, \"to\": 8444}, {\"ngram\": \"Skinner\", \"from\": 8461, \"to\": 8468}, {\"ngram\": \"all social media platforms\", \"from\": 8472, \"to\": 8498}, {\"ngram\": \"the comments\", \"from\": 8504, \"to\": 8516}, {\"ngram\": \"their mark\", \"from\": 8530, \"to\": 8540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Biles' recent Instagram post which references Skinner's comment, Olympic teammate McKayla Moroney remarked, \\\"It does not get more iconic than this.. She f'd around n found out\\\" [sic].\", \"from\": 8543, \"to\": 8729, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8560, \"end\": 8569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9078096870733906e-69, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 8628, \"end\": 8635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McKayla_Maroney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"McKayla\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McKayla_Maroney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McKayla_Maroney\"}, {\"begin\": 8636, \"end\": 8643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Moroney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.682871942729212e-16, \"text\": \"Moroney\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Moroney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Moroney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Skinner's comment\", \"from\": 8592, \"to\": 8609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"F around and find out\\\" has become the gymnastic team's unofficial nickname, with Biles leaving a press conference in fits of laughter after revealing the not safe for work moniker.\", \"from\": 8731, \"to\": 8912, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"F\", \"from\": 8732, \"to\": 8733}, {\"ngram\": \"the gymnastic team's unofficial nickname\", \"from\": 8766, \"to\": 8806}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 8813, \"to\": 8818}, {\"ngram\": \"a press conference\", \"from\": 8827, \"to\": 8845}, {\"ngram\": \"fits\", \"from\": 8849, \"to\": 8853}, {\"ngram\": \"laughter\", \"from\": 8857, \"to\": 8865}, {\"ngram\": \"work moniker\", \"from\": 8899, \"to\": 8911}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It did not come out of nowhere: it's a long-standing tradition for the United States women's gymnastic team to give themselves a nickname after winning gold.\", \"from\": 8913, \"to\": 9070, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8984, \"end\": 8997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999985760933802, \"rank\": 1.2697415660937933e-06, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long-standing tradition\", \"from\": 8950, \"to\": 8975}, {\"ngram\": \"a nickname\", \"from\": 9040, \"to\": 9050}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 9065, \"to\": 9069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 1996 it was The Magnificent Seven.\", \"from\": 9071, \"to\": 9108, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Magnificent Seven\", \"from\": 9086, \"to\": 9107}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2012 it was The Fierce Five.\", \"from\": 9109, \"to\": 9140, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Fierce Five\", \"from\": 9124, \"to\": 9139}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, it seems Biles is demonstrating her hallmark wit and candour by revealing the tongue-in-cheek name.\", \"from\": 9141, \"to\": 9251, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 9161, \"to\": 9166}, {\"ngram\": \"her hallmark wit\", \"from\": 9184, \"to\": 9200}, {\"ngram\": \"candour\", \"from\": 9205, \"to\": 9212}, {\"ngram\": \"cheek\", \"from\": 9240, \"to\": 9245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles has been open about having therapy since her setback in 2020.\", \"from\": 9253, \"to\": 9320, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 9253, \"to\": 9258}, {\"ngram\": \"therapy\", \"from\": 9286, \"to\": 9293}, {\"ngram\": \"her setback\", \"from\": 9300, \"to\": 9311}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She told USA Today: \\\"I thought I could figure it out on my own, but that's sometimes not the case.\", \"from\": 9321, \"to\": 9419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9330, \"end\": 9339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.307544768075339e-43, \"text\": \"USA Today\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 9410, \"to\": 9418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I actually enjoyed it and looked forward to going to therapy.\", \"from\": 9420, \"to\": 9481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"therapy\", \"from\": 9473, \"to\": 9480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a safe space.\\\"\", \"from\": 9482, \"to\": 9501, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a safe space\", \"from\": 9487, \"to\": 9499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now competing in Paris, Biles has made a magnificent comeback on the world stage.\", \"from\": 9503, \"to\": 9584, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9520, \"end\": 9525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.348858403329773e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 9527, \"to\": 9532}, {\"ngram\": \"a magnificent comeback\", \"from\": 9542, \"to\": 9564}, {\"ngram\": \"the world stage\", \"from\": 9568, \"to\": 9583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has stunned audiences with her complex and demanding routines as part of the team competition, and will be competing in the women's all-round final on August 1, the women's vault final on August 3, the women's uneven bars final on August 4, and the women's balance beam final and floor final on August 5.\", \"from\": 9585, \"to\": 9893, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"audiences\", \"from\": 9601, \"to\": 9610}, {\"ngram\": \"her complex and demanding routines\", \"from\": 9616, \"to\": 9650}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 9654, \"to\": 9658}, {\"ngram\": \"the team competition\", \"from\": 9662, \"to\": 9682}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's all-round final\", \"from\": 9709, \"to\": 9736}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 9740, \"to\": 9746}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 9777, \"to\": 9783}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's uneven bars\", \"from\": 9787, \"to\": 9810}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 9820, \"to\": 9826}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's balance beam\", \"from\": 9834, \"to\": 9858}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 9884, \"to\": 9890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If she wins gold in all of her upcoming events, she has the exciting chance to achieve the record of most Olympic gold medals by any gymnast, male or female, in history.\", \"from\": 9895, \"to\": 10064, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 9907, \"to\": 9911}, {\"ngram\": \"her upcoming events\", \"from\": 9922, \"to\": 9941}, {\"ngram\": \"the exciting chance\", \"from\": 9951, \"to\": 9970}, {\"ngram\": \"the record\", \"from\": 9982, \"to\": 9992}, {\"ngram\": \"most Olympic gold medals\", \"from\": 9996, \"to\": 10020}, {\"ngram\": \"any gymnast\", \"from\": 10024, \"to\": 10035}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 10056, \"to\": 10063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That record is currently held by former Soviet artistic gymnast, Larisa Latynina.\", \"from\": 10065, \"to\": 10146, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10105, \"end\": 10111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soviet_Union\", \"score\": 0.9999999996907718, \"rank\": 2.908572825874603e-10, \"text\": \"Soviet\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soviet_Union\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soviet_Union\"}, {\"begin\": 10130, \"end\": 10145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Larisa Latynina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That record\", \"from\": 10065, \"to\": 10076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles currently has five Olympic golds to her name, with the record sitting at nine.\", \"from\": 10147, \"to\": 10231, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 10147, \"to\": 10152}, {\"ngram\": \"five Olympic golds\", \"from\": 10167, \"to\": 10185}, {\"ngram\": \"her name\", \"from\": 1018